{"tid":1591461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勿過度關注懷疑被自殺事件","createTime":"2019-09-24T07:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T08:02:38.000Z","uid":242623,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"23520e01ed8dacfed12f6c1c30ee03882cb82e1b","tid":1591461,"uid":242623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:09:24.000Z","msg":"我知大家都好嬲，亦都覺得好恐怖，不過其實呢啲嘢無可能靠我地係度討論而fc到，除非有人影到班狗棄屍/家屬出黎講。<br />\n<br />\n有人可能會話班狗冇人性，咩都做得出，唔好覺得被自殺唔會發生。就算我地信都好，有200萬人信都好，呢啲未有實質證據嘅嘢都係做唔到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線</span></span>嘅彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n我地仲有好多已fc嘅核彈未用，點解唔煲大嗰啲做下文宣先？<br />\n<br />\n宜家完全比荃灣浮屍單嘢洗晒版，行動post又推唔郁，我覺得無謂再為左啲fc唔到嘅嘢而討論咁多，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中一個post</span></span>討論就ok，有真&middot;fc嘅料再開post都未遲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4sJEi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4sJEi1.jpg&h=a7f7a49c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2275bb9b57408d5e0fda578c7d11c06c23190e2","tid":1591461,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Q1RNV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Q1RNV6.jpg&h=227effc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bf0acde8c8a47821a37d857003fe93fa82a5ceb","tid":1591461,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"但換個角度<br />\n有核陣爆起大家出黎既意欲係會大左<br />\n<br />\n前題係大家要知黎緊日程 所以行動post 都好緊要"},{"pid":"67e4adb6f82e927c07c622ba7efaded5394cab9f","tid":1591461,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:20:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d350a67ff7a51f7a513321ffb056532befadcf33","tid":1591461,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:02:38.000Z","msg":"push"}]}